description: Fat Mikes Gourmet Grub is a classic Pub Grub food truck with a southern twist. We feature gourmet burgers and hot dogs with a variety of toppings, as well as a Philly steak and cheese that is our biggest seller.  In addition to burgers and hot dogs we also serve southern fried delights which include Fried Green Beans, Fried Mac-n-Cheese, and Fried Pickles, Mozzarella Sticks, Cheddar Cheese Jalapeno Poppers, and Sweet Potato Fries. All of which is sure to have you feeling right at home!
name: Fat Mike's Gourmet Grub
